WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.18.0.0

00:00:14.226 --> 00:00:15.215
No way

00:00:29.133 --> 00:00:31.428
Did I… do it

00:00:31.512 --> 00:00:32.753
with a guy yesterday?

00:00:42.299 --> 00:00:44.226
He's so handsome
It's annoying

00:01:19.830 --> 00:01:21.085
[Kuroda Naoya
Half-brother]

00:01:21.168 --> 00:01:22.416
[Kuroda Misaki
Naoya's wife]

00:01:24.304 --> 00:01:25.460
Were you already home?

00:01:29.353 --> 00:01:32.224
That trillion yen
contract with Toei

00:01:32.808 --> 00:01:35.045
Whoever seals that deal
will be made successor

00:01:35.129 --> 00:01:36.885
is what Father said

00:01:36.969 --> 00:01:37.889
So?

00:01:37.973 --> 00:01:39.433
Chairman of Toei

00:01:39.663 --> 00:01:40.875
won't even sit

00:01:40.959 --> 00:01:43.478
at the negotiation table
if you're not a married man

00:01:43.679 --> 00:01:47.190
He says he can't trust
an unmarried man

00:01:47.274 --> 00:01:49.401
Mr. Koichi is
still single, right?

00:01:49.837 --> 00:01:52.506
Not only is he not married
but he has no scandals

00:01:52.590 --> 00:01:55.198
You don't like being
touched by others, right?

00:01:55.282 --> 00:01:57.326
Are you still

00:01:57.882 --> 00:01:59.008
a virgin?

00:02:02.807 --> 00:02:04.435
Mind your own business

00:02:04.626 --> 00:02:06.337
Don't push yourself too hard

00:02:06.595 --> 00:02:08.170
Don't you worry

00:02:08.439 --> 00:02:10.088
It's less than two weeks now

00:02:10.614 --> 00:02:13.133
What are you going to do
without a partner?

00:02:13.550 --> 00:02:14.301
I do

00:02:15.983 --> 00:02:17.068
I never said I didn't

00:02:21.071 --> 00:02:23.696
Who would stay with
someone as heartless as you?

00:02:24.196 --> 00:02:26.750
You've never been
loved by anyone

